## How Long Does SEO Take for Reading Businesses?

| Scope | Typical Timeline |
|-------|-----------------|
| Technical fixes (crawling, indexing) | 4-8 weeks |
| Local SEO (Google Maps, "near me") | 3-6 months |
| Competitive organic authority | 6-12 months |
| Highly competitive national terms | 12+ months |

The first 3-6 months establish foundations. Months 6-12 show accelerating returns as topical authority compounds. This timeline is the same whether you use an SEO agency or consultant — it's set by Google's evaluation cycles, not headcount.

