## What If Previous SEO Didn't Work?

Most failed SEO stems from three patterns:

- **Generic advice** — no understanding of Reading's competitive landscape
- **Thin content** — ticking keyword boxes without building topical authority
- **No strategy** — chasing isolated keywords instead of building interconnected content networks

If an agency or SEO company didn't deliver results for your Reading business, it was almost certainly a **methodology problem**, not an SEO problem. A data-led approach with local market knowledge and systematic authority building changes the trajectory within 6-12 months.

